<text><body>
<lb n="0781a20"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0781a21"/>
<lb n="0781a22"/><head type="no">No. 512</head>
<lb n="0781a23"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead>佛說淨飯王般涅槃經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0781a24"/>
<lb n="0781a25"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0781004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔宋居…譯〕－【聖】</note><app n="0781004" word-count="8"><lem>宋居士沮渠京聲譯</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0781a26"/><div1 type="jing"><p>如是我聞。一時佛住王舍城耆闍崛山中。與
<lb n="0781a27"/>大比丘眾俱。爾時世尊。光明&CB02368;&CB02368;。喻若日
<lb n="0781a28"/>出照明世間。時舍夷國王。名曰淨飯。治以
<lb n="0781a29"/>正法。禮德<note n="0781005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仁義＝二儀【聖】</note><app n="0781005"><lem>仁義</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">二儀</rdg></app>。常行慈心。時被重病。身中
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0512.0781b" n="0781b"/>
<lb n="0781b01"/>四大。同時俱作。殘害其<note n="0781006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">體＝身【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0781006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">體＝身【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0781006"><lem>體</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">身</rdg></app>。支節欲解。喘息
<lb n="0781b02"/>不定。如駛水流。輔相宣令國中明醫。皆悉
<lb n="0781b03"/>集會。瞻王所疾。隨病授藥。種種療治。無能
<lb n="0781b04"/>愈者。瑞應<note n="0781007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝以【聖】＊</note><note n="0781007" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>已＝以【聖】＊</note><app n="0781007"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>至。將死不久。時王煩<note n="0781008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">躁＝燥【聖】</note><app n="0781008"><lem>躁</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">燥</rdg></app>。轉
<lb n="0781b05"/>側不<note n="0781009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">停＝亭【聖】</note><app n="0781009"><lem>停</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">亭</rdg></app>。如少水魚夫人<note n="0781010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婇＝採【聖】</note><app n="0781010"><lem>婇</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">採</rdg></app>女。見其如是。益
<lb n="0781b06"/>更愁惱。時白飯王。<note n="0781011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔斛飯王〕－【宮】</note><app n="0781011"><lem>斛飯王</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。大稱王等。及諸
<lb n="0781b07"/>群臣。同發聲言。今王設崩。永失覆護。國將
<lb n="0781b08"/>虛弱。王身戰動。脣口乾燥。語聲數絕。<note n="0781012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">眩目＝玄置【聖】</note><app n="0781012"><lem>眩目</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">玄置</rdg></app>
<lb n="0781b09"/>淚下。時諸王等。皆以敬意。長跪叉手。同共
<lb n="0781b10"/>白言。大王素性。不好作惡。經彈指頃。積德
<lb n="0781b11"/>無厭。護養人民。莫不得安。名聞十方。大王
<lb n="0781b12"/>今日。何故愁惱。時淨飯王。語聲<note n="0781013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">輒＝趣【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0781013"><lem>輒</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">趣</rdg></app>出。告
<lb n="0781b13"/>諸王曰。<note n="0781014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">我命雖逝＝我令雖斷【宮】</note><app n="0781014"><lem>我命雖逝</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">我令雖斷</rdg></app>。不以為苦。但恨不見我
<lb n="0781b14"/>子悉達。又恨不見次子難陀。<note n="0781015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＝已【三】【宮】</note><note n="0781015" resp="CBETA" type="mod">以＝已【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781015"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">已</rdg></app>除貪婬世
<lb n="0781b15"/>間諸欲。復恨不見<note n="0781016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">斛飯王＝縠飯王【宮】＊</note><app n="0781016"><lem>斛飯王</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">縠飯王</rdg></app>子阿難陀者。持
<lb n="0781b16"/>佛法藏。一言不失。又恨不見孫子羅<note n="0781017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">云＝雲【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0781017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">云＝雲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0781017"><lem>云</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">雲</rdg></app>。年
<lb n="0781b17"/>雖幼稚。神足純備。戒行無缺。吾設得見是
<lb n="0781b18"/>諸子等。我病雖篤。未離生死。不以為苦。諸
<lb n="0781b19"/>在王邊。聞如是語。莫不啼泣。淚下如雨。時
<lb n="0781b20"/>白飯王。<note n="0781018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">答＝白【三】【宮】</note><note n="0781018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">答＝白【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781018"><lem>答</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">白</rdg></app>淨飯王言。我聞世尊。在王舍城
<lb n="0781b21"/>耆闍崛山中。去此<note n="0781019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">懸＝玄【聖】＊</note><app n="0781019"><lem>懸</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">玄</rdg></app>遠。五十由旬。王今轉
<lb n="0781b22"/>羸。設遣使者。道路<note n="0781020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">懸邈＝懸遠【三】【宮】，玄邈【聖】</note><note n="0781020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">懸邈＝懸遠【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝玄邈【聖】</note><app n="0781020"><lem>懸邈</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">懸遠</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">玄邈</rdg></app>。懼恐遲晚。無所加
<lb n="0781b23"/>益<note n="0781021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【三】【宮】下同</note><note n="0781021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">唯＝惟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】下同</note><app n="0781021"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>願大王。莫大愁悒<app type="＊" source="0781019"><lem>懸</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">玄</rdg></app>念諸子。時淨飯
<lb n="0781b24"/>王。聞是語已。垂淚而言。答白飯王。我子等
<lb n="0781b25"/>輩。雖復遼遠。意望不斷。所以者何。我子成
<lb n="0781b26"/>佛。以大慈悲。&M010527;以神通。天眼徹視。天耳洞
<lb n="0781b27"/>聽。救接眾生應可度者。如有百千萬億眾生。
<lb n="0781b28"/>為水所溺。以慈愍心。為作船筏。而度脫之。
<lb n="0781b29"/>終不勞疲。譬如有人為賊所圍。或值怨敵惶
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0512.0781c" n="0781c"/>
<lb n="0781c01"/>怖失計。不望自濟。唯求救護。依有勢者。欲
<lb n="0781c02"/>從<note n="0781022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恐＝怨【聖】</note><app n="0781022"><lem>恐</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">怨</rdg></app>難而得解脫。譬<note n="0781023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如＝若【三】【宮】</note><note n="0781023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如＝若【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781023"><lem>如</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">若</rdg></app>有人時得重病。欲
<lb n="0781c03"/>得良醫以療其疾。如我今日。望見世尊。亦
<lb n="0781c04"/>復如是。所以然者。世尊晝夜。常以三時。&M010527;
<lb n="0781c05"/>以天眼。觀於眾生應受化者。以慈<note n="0781024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">愍＝悲【三】【宮】</note><note n="0781024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">愍＝悲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781024"><lem>愍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">悲</rdg></app>心。如
<lb n="0781c06"/>母念子。爾時世尊在靈鷲山。天耳遙聞。迦
<lb n="0781c07"/><note n="0781025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">維＝惟【聖】</note><app n="0781025"><lem>維</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>羅<note n="0781026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">衛＝越【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0781026" resp="CBETA" type="mod">衛＝越【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0781026"><lem>衛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">越</rdg></app>大城之中。父王悒遲。及諸王言。即
<lb n="0781c08"/>以天眼。遙見父王。病臥著床羸困憔悴命欲
<lb n="0781c09"/>向終。知父渴仰欲見諸子</p>
<lb n="0781c10"/><p>爾時世尊告難陀曰。父王淨飯。勝世間王。是
<lb n="0781c11"/>我曹父。今得重病。宜當往見。餘命少在。時
<lb n="0781c12"/>嚴<note n="0781027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">速＝欲【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0781027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">速＝欲【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0781027"><lem>速</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">欲</rdg></app>發。我曹應往。<note n="0781028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">及＝曼【三】</note><note n="0781028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">及＝曼【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0781028"><lem>及</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">曼</rdg></app>命存在。<note n="0781029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得與＝及共【三】【宮】</note><note n="0781029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">得與＝及共【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0781029"><lem>得與</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">及共</rdg></app>相見。
<lb n="0781c13"/>令王願滿。難陀受教。長跪作禮。唯然世尊。
<lb n="0781c14"/>淨飯王者。是我曹父。所作奇特。能生聖子。
<lb n="0781c15"/>利益世間。今宜往詣。報育養恩。阿難合掌。
<lb n="0781c16"/>前白佛言。我隨世尊。<note n="0781030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">貪＝會【三】</note><note n="0781030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">貪＝會【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0781030"><lem>貪</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">會</rdg></app>共相見。淨飯王者。
<lb n="0781c17"/>是我伯父。聽我出家為佛弟子。得佛為師。是
<lb n="0781c18"/>故欲往。羅<app type="＊" source="0781017"><lem>云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雲</rdg></app>復前而白佛言。世尊。雖是我
<lb n="0781c19"/>父。棄國求道。我蒙祖王育養成就。而得出
<lb n="0781c20"/>家。是故欲往奉覲祖王。佛言。善哉善哉。宜
<lb n="0781c21"/>知是時。令王願滿</p>
<lb n="0781c22"/><p>於<note n="0781031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">是＝時【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0781031" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo type="＊"/>是＝時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0781031"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">時</rdg></app>世尊。即以神足。猶如<note n="0781032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鴈＝鷹【宮】</note><app n="0781032"><lem>鴈</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">鷹</rdg></app>王。<note n="0781033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">踊＝躍【聖】</note><app n="0781033"><lem>踊</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">躍</rdg></app>身虛
<lb n="0781c23"/>空。忽然而現在<note n="0781034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">迦維＝迦惟【宋】【元】【宮】，加惟【聖】</note><note n="0781034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">迦維＝迦惟【宋】【元】【宮】，＝加惟【聖】</note><app n="0781034"><lem>迦維</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">迦惟</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">加惟</rdg></app>羅衛。放大光明。國中
<lb n="0781c24"/>人民。遙見佛來。皆共舉聲。涕淚而言。設大
<lb n="0781c25"/>王崩。舍夷國名必<note n="0781035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">絕＝斷【三】【宮】，逝【聖】</note><note n="0781035" resp="CBETA" type="mod">絕＝斷【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝逝【聖】</note><app n="0781035"><lem>絕</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">斷</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">逝</rdg></app>滅矣。城中人民。向佛
<lb n="0781c26"/>啼哭。白世尊<note n="0781036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔言〕－【聖】</note><app n="0781036"><lem>言</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。爾時太子。踰出宮城。詣藍
<lb n="0781c27"/>毘樹下。而坐思惟。父王見之。稽首敬禮。大
<lb n="0781c28"/>王如是。命斷不久。唯願如來。宜可時往及
<lb n="0781c29"/>共相見。國中人民。宛轉自撲。哽咽啼哭。中
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0512.0782a" n="0782a"/>
<lb n="0782a01"/>有自絕瓔珞<note n="0782001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（之）＋者【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0782001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（之）＋者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0782001"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">之者</rdg></app>。中有自裂壞衣服<app type="＊" source="0782001"><lem>者</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">之者</rdg></app>。中有
<lb n="0782a02"/><note n="0782002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（自&CB00235;…者）十五字＝取灰土而自坌者中有自&CB00235;拔其髮者【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">（自&CB00235;…者）十五字＝取灰土而自坌者中有自&CB00235;拔其髮者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782002" word-count="15"><lem>自<note n="0782003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00235;＝縱【聖】</note><app n="0782003"><lem>&CB00235;</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">縱</rdg></app>拔其髮者。中有取灰土而自坌者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">取灰土而自坌者中有自&CB00235;拔其髮者</rdg></app>。痛
<lb n="0782a03"/>徹骨髓。猶顛狂人。佛見是已。諫國中人。無
<lb n="0782a04"/>常<note n="0782004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">別離＝離別【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">別離＝離別【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782004"><lem>別離</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">離別</rdg></app>古今有是。汝等諸人。當思念之。生
<lb n="0782a05"/>死為苦。唯道是真。佛以法雨。灌眾<note n="0782005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">生＝惱【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">生＝惱【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782005"><lem>生</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">惱</rdg></app>心。
<lb n="0782a06"/>以種種法。而開解之</p>
<lb n="0782a07"/><p>於是世尊。即以十力四無所畏十八不共諸
<lb n="0782a08"/>佛之法。放大光明。更復重以三十二相八十
<lb n="0782a09"/>種好。放大光明。<anchor id="fxT14p0782a02"/>以從無量阿僧祇劫。所作
<lb n="0782a10"/>功德。放大光明。其光照曜。內外通達。周遍
<lb n="0782a11"/>國界。光照王身。患苦得安。王遂怪言。是何
<lb n="0782a12"/>光<note n="0782006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耶＝也【聖】</note><app n="0782006"><lem>耶</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">也</rdg></app>。為<note n="0782007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">日月光＝是日月光明耶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782007" resp="CBETA" type="mod">日月光＝是日月光明耶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782007"><lem>日月光</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">是日月光明耶</rdg></app>諸天光乎。光觸我身。如
<lb n="0782a13"/><note n="0782008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＝入【宮】</note><app n="0782008"><lem>天</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">入</rdg></app>栴檀。令我身中患苦得息。我遂疑怪<note n="0782009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">儻＝脫【聖】</note><app n="0782009"><lem>儻</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">脫</rdg></app>
<lb n="0782a14"/>是我子。悉達來<note n="0782010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">也＝耶【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">也＝耶【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782010"><lem>也</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">耶</rdg></app>。先現光明。是其瑞<note n="0782011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">耳＝也【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0782011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">耳＝也【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0782011"><lem>耳</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">也</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0782a15"/>時大稱王。從外入宮。白大王言。世尊<note n="0782012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已來＝來也【三】【宮】，以來【聖】</note><note n="0782012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已來＝來也【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝以來【聖】</note><app n="0782012"><lem>已來</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">來也</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">以來</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0782a16"/>將諸弟子。阿難難陀羅<app type="＊" source="0781017"><lem>云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雲</rdg></app>之等。乘<note n="0782013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">空＝虛【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">空＝虛【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782013"><lem>空</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">虛</rdg></app>來至。
<lb n="0782a17"/>王宜歡喜。捨愁毒心。王聞佛來。敬意踊躍。
<lb n="0782a18"/>不覺起坐。須臾之頃。佛便入宮。王見佛到。
<lb n="0782a19"/><note n="0782014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遙＝豫【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">遙＝豫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782014"><lem>遙</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">豫</rdg></app>舉兩手。接足而言。唯願如來。手觸我身。
<lb n="0782a20"/>令我得安。為病所困。如<note n="0782015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">壓＝押【聖】</note><app n="0782015"><lem>壓</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">押</rdg></app>麻油。痛不可忍。
<lb n="0782a21"/>我命將<note n="0782016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">逝＝斷【宮】</note><app n="0782016"><lem>逝</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">斷</rdg></app>。寧可還反。我今最後。得見世尊。
<lb n="0782a22"/>痛<note n="0782017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恨＝既【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">恨＝既【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782017"><lem>恨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">既</rdg></app>即除。佛知父王病重羸瘦。色變難識。
<lb n="0782a23"/>&CB00418;見<note n="0782018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">形＝刑【聖】</note><app n="0782018"><lem>形</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">刑</rdg></app>體。憔悴叵<note n="0782019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">看＋（佛）【聖】</note><app n="0782019"><lem>看</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">看佛</rdg></app>。佛告難陀。觀王本
<lb n="0782a24"/>時。形體巍巍。<note n="0782020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">顏＝妙【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">顏＝妙【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782020"><lem>顏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">妙</rdg></app>色端正。名聲遠聞。今得重
<lb n="0782a25"/>病。乃不可識。端正形容。勇健之名。今何所
<lb n="0782a26"/>在。爾時淨飯王。一心合掌。歎世尊言</p>
<lb n="0782a27"/><lg><l>汝願已成就</l><l>亦滿眾生願</l>
<lb n="0782a28"/><l>我今得重病</l><l>願佛度我厄</l>
<lb n="0782a29"/><l>嚴飾瞿曇種</l><l>汝為甚奇特</l>
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0512.0782b" n="0782b"/>
<lb n="0782b01"/><l>末世說正法</l><l>無護而作護</l>
<lb n="0782b02"/><l>法王以法味</l><l>灌<note n="0782021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">澤＝濯【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">澤＝濯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782021"><lem>澤</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">濯</rdg></app>諸眾生</l>
<lb n="0782b03"/><l>如是後<note n="0782022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世人＝聖王【三】【宮】，聖人【聖】</note><note n="0782022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">世人＝聖王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝聖人【聖】</note><app n="0782022"><lem>世人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">聖王</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">聖人</rdg></app></l><l>我子極慈孝</l>
<lb n="0782b04"/><l>人中之上寶</l><l>名達大千界</l>
<lb n="0782b05"/><l>上至淨居天</l><l>獨步無等雙</l></lg>
<lb n="0782b06"/><p>佛言。唯願父王。莫復愁<note n="0782023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悒＝憂【三】【宮】，邑【聖】</note><note n="0782023" resp="CBETA" type="mod">悒＝憂【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝邑【聖】</note><app n="0782023"><lem>悒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">憂</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">邑</rdg></app>。所以然者。道德
<lb n="0782b07"/>純備。無有缺減。佛從袈裟&M034294;出金色臂。掌
<lb n="0782b08"/>如蓮華。即以手著父王額上。王是清淨。戒
<lb n="0782b09"/>行之人。心垢<note n="0782024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝以【宮】</note><app n="0782024"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>離。今應歡悅。不宜煩惱。當
<lb n="0782b10"/>諦思念。諸經法義。於不牢固。得堅固志。<note n="0782025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">已＝以【三】【聖】＊【宮】</note><note n="0782025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">已＝以【宋】【元】【明】【聖】＊【宮】</note><app n="0782025"><lem>已</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【聖】【宮】" resp="Taisho">以</rdg></app>
<lb n="0782b11"/>種善根。是故大王。宜當<note n="0782026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">歡＝觀【聖】</note><app n="0782026"><lem>歡</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">觀</rdg></app>喜。命雖欲終。自
<lb n="0782b12"/>可寬意。時大稱王。以恭敬<note n="0782027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＝意【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782027" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心＝意【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782027"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">意</rdg></app>。白淨飯王言。
<lb n="0782b13"/>佛是王子。神力具足。無與等者。次子難陀。
<lb n="0782b14"/>亦是王子。已度生死諸欲之海。四道無礙。
<lb n="0782b15"/><app type="＊" source="0781016"><lem>斛飯王</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宮】">縠飯王</rdg></app>子。阿難陀者。<app type="＊" source="0782025"><lem>已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">以</rdg></app>服法味。佛所說
<lb n="0782b16"/>法。猶<note n="0782028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若＝如【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">若＝如【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782028"><lem>若</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">如</rdg></app>淵海。一句不忘。悉總持之。王孫羅
<lb n="0782b17"/><app type="＊" source="0781017"><lem>云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雲</rdg></app>。道德純備。逮諸禪定。成四道果。是四
<lb n="0782b18"/>子等。<app type="＊" source="0782025"><lem>已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">以</rdg></app>壞魔網。時淨飯王。聞是語已。歡喜
<lb n="0782b19"/>踊躍。不能自勝。即以自手。捉於佛手。著其
<lb n="0782b20"/>心上。王於臥處。<note n="0782029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔仰向…處〕八十字－【聖】</note><app n="0782029" word-count="80"><lem>仰向合掌。白世尊言。我瞻
<lb n="0782b21"/>如來。目<note n="0782030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00263;不眴＝睫不瞬【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00263;不眴＝睫不瞬【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782030"><lem>&CB00263;不眴</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">睫不瞬</rdg></app>。視之無厭。我願已滿。心意
<lb n="0782b22"/>踊躍。從是<note n="0782031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">取＝臥【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782031" resp="CBETA" type="mod">取＝臥【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782031"><lem>取</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">臥</rdg></app>別。如來至真。多所<note n="0782032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">饒＝利【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">饒＝利【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782032"><lem>饒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">利</rdg></app>益。其
<lb n="0782b23"/>有得見。聞所說者。此輩之等皆是有相。大
<lb n="0782b24"/>功德人。今日世尊。是我之子。接遇過多。不
<lb n="0782b25"/>見捐棄。王於臥處</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。合掌心禮世尊足下。時
<lb n="0782b26"/>佛手掌。故在王<note n="0782033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">心＋（上）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">心＋（上）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782033"><lem>心</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">心上</rdg></app>。無常對至。命盡氣絕。忽
<lb n="0782b27"/>就後世。於是諸釋。<note n="0782034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02856;＝號【明】</note><app n="0782034"><lem>&CB02856;</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">號</rdg></app>咷啼哭。舉身自撲。兩
<lb n="0782b28"/>手拍地。解<note n="0782035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">髻＝結【聖】</note><app n="0782035"><lem>髻</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">結</rdg></app>亂髮。同發聲言。永失覆蓋。<note n="0782036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔中〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782036" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔中〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782036"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0782b29"/>有自絕<note n="0782037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">瓔＝纓【聖】</note><app n="0782037"><lem>瓔</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">纓</rdg></app>珞<note n="0782038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔者〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782038" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔者〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782038"><lem>者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。中有<note n="0782039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔自〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782039" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔自〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782039"><lem>自</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>裂壞衣<note n="0782040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">服＋（之）【三】，服＝嚴之【宮】</note><note n="0782040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">服＋（之）【宋】【元】【明】，服＝嚴之【宮】</note><app n="0782040"><lem>服</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">服之</rdg><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">嚴之</rdg></app>者。<note n="0782041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔中有…者〕九字－【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0782041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔中有…者〕九字－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0782041" word-count="9"><lem>中
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0512.0782c" n="0782c"/>
<lb n="0782c01"/>有取灰土而自坌者</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。<note n="0782042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔中〕－【宮】</note><app n="0782042"><lem>中</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>有自<note n="0782043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">總＝&CB00235;【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782043" resp="CBETA" type="mod">總＝&CB00235;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782043"><lem>總</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB00235;</rdg></app>拔其髮者。
<lb n="0782c02"/><note n="0782044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔中有…有〕十五字－【聖】</note><note n="0782044" resp="CBETA" type="mod">中有說王順政治國不枉人民者中有復＝復【聖】</note><app n="0782044"><lem>中有說王順<note n="0782045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">政＝正【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782045" resp="CBETA" type="mod">政＝正【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782045"><lem>政</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">正</rdg></app>治國不枉人民者。中<note n="0782046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">有復＝復有【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782046" resp="CBETA" type="mod">有復＝復有【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782046"><lem>有復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">復有</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">復</rdg></app>
<lb n="0782c03"/>言。諸小國等。失其覆護。王中尊王。今已崩
<lb n="0782c04"/><note n="0782047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">背＝皆【聖】</note><app n="0782047"><lem>背</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">皆</rdg></app>。國失威神。時諸釋子。以眾香汁。洗浴王
<lb n="0782c05"/>身。纏以劫<note n="0782048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">波＝婆【聖】</note><app n="0782048"><lem>波</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">婆</rdg></app>育<note n="0782049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00626;＝疊【聖】</note><app n="0782049"><lem>&CB00626;</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">疊</rdg></app>及諸繒<note n="0782050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">帛＝綵【聖】</note><app n="0782050"><lem>帛</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">綵</rdg></app>。而以棺斂。
<lb n="0782c06"/><note n="0782051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">作＝於【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">作＝於【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782051"><lem>作</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">於</rdg></app>師子座。七寶莊<note n="0782052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">挍＝嚴【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782052" resp="CBETA" type="mod">挍＝嚴【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782052"><lem>挍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">嚴</rdg></app>。真珠羅網。垂繞其
<lb n="0782c07"/>傍。<note n="0782053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔便〕－【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0782053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔便〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0782053"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>舉棺<note n="0782054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">置＝著【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">置＝著【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782054"><lem>置</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">著</rdg></app>於師子座上。散華燒香。佛共
<lb n="0782c08"/>難陀。在喪頭前肅恭而立。阿難羅云。住在
<lb n="0782c09"/>喪足。難陀長跪。白佛言。父王養我。願聽難
<lb n="0782c10"/>陀擔父王棺。阿難合掌。前白佛言。唯願聽
<lb n="0782c11"/>我擔伯父棺。羅<app type="＊" source="0781017"><lem>云</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">雲</rdg></app>復前而白佛言。<note n="0782055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔唯〕－【宮】</note><app n="0782055"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>願聽
<lb n="0782c12"/>我擔<note n="0782056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">祖王＝父王【聖】</note><app n="0782056"><lem>祖王</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">父王</rdg></app>棺</p>
<lb n="0782c13"/><p>爾時世尊。念當來世。人民兇暴。不報父母
<lb n="0782c14"/>育養之恩。為<note n="0782057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782057"><lem>是</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>不孝之者。為是當來眾生
<lb n="0782c15"/>之等。設禮法故。如來躬身。自欲擔於父王
<lb n="0782c16"/>之棺。即時三千大千世界。六種震動。一切
<lb n="0782c17"/><note n="0782058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">眾山&CB01064;&CB01173;＝諸山岠峨【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782058" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眾山&CB01064;&CB01173;＝諸山岠峨【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782058"><lem>眾山。&CB01064;&CB01173;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">諸山岠峨</rdg></app>涌沒。如水上船。爾時欲界。一切
<lb n="0782c18"/>諸天。與無央數百千眷屬。俱來赴喪。北方
<lb n="0782c19"/>天<note n="0782059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王毘沙門＝毘沙門王【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782059" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王毘沙門＝毘沙門王【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782059"><lem>王毘沙門</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">毘沙門王</rdg></app>。將諸夜叉鬼神之等。億百千
<lb n="0782c20"/>眾。俱來赴喪。東方天王提頭賴吒。從諸伎
<lb n="0782c21"/>樂鬼神之等。億百千眾。俱來赴喪。南方天
<lb n="0782c22"/>王毘<note n="0782060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">樓＝留【三】【宮】</note><note n="0782060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">樓＝留【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0782060"><lem>樓</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">留</rdg></app>勒叉。<note n="0782061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">從＝將【宮】</note><app n="0782061"><lem>從</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">將</rdg></app><note n="0782062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鳩＝究【聖】</note><app n="0782062"><lem>鳩</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">究</rdg></app>槃荼鬼神之等。億百千
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0512.0783a" n="0783a"/>
<lb n="0783a01"/>眾。俱來赴喪西方天王毘留<note n="0783001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婆＝博【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783001" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婆＝博【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783001"><lem>婆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">博</rdg></app>叉。<note n="0783002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">從＝將【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783002" resp="CBETA" type="mod">從＝將【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783002"><lem>從</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">將</rdg></app>諸龍
<lb n="0783a02"/>神。億百千眾。俱來赴喪。皆共發哀。舉聲啼
<lb n="0783a03"/>哭。時四天王。竊共<note n="0783003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">思＝私【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783003" resp="CBETA" type="mod">思＝私【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783003"><lem>思</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">私</rdg></app>議。瞻望世尊。為當來
<lb n="0783a04"/>世諸不孝順父母者故。以大慈悲。現自躬身
<lb n="0783a05"/>擔父王棺。時四天王。<note n="0783004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">俱共＝同時【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">俱共＝同時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783004"><lem>俱共</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">同時</rdg></app>長跪。<note n="0783005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔同時發聲〕－【宮】</note><app n="0783005"><lem>同時發
<lb n="0783a06"/>聲</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。俱白佛言。唯然世尊。願聽我等擔父王
<lb n="0783a07"/>棺。所以然者。我等亦是佛之弟子。<note n="0783006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔亦復〕－【聖】</note><app n="0783006"><lem>亦復</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>從
<lb n="0783a08"/>佛。聞法意解。得法眼淨。成須陀洹。以是之
<lb n="0783a09"/>故。我曹<note n="0783007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宜＝儀【聖】</note><app n="0783007"><lem>宜</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">儀</rdg></app>擔父王之棺</p>
<lb n="0783a10"/><p>爾時世尊。聽四天王擔父王棺。時四天王。各
<lb n="0783a11"/>自變身。如人形像。以手擎棺。擔在肩上。舉
<lb n="0783a12"/>國人民。一切大眾。莫不啼哭</p>
<lb n="0783a13"/><p>爾時世尊。威光益顯。如萬日並。如來躬身。
<lb n="0783a14"/>手執香爐。在喪前行。出詣葬所。靈鷲山上。
<lb n="0783a15"/>有千阿羅漢。以神足力。乘虛來<note n="0783008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">至＝詣【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783008" resp="CBETA" type="mod">至＝詣【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783008"><lem>至</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">詣</rdg></app>。稽首佛
<lb n="0783a16"/>足。復白佛言。唯願世尊。&CB00330;使何事。時佛便
<lb n="0783a17"/>告<note n="0783009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔諸〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔諸〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783009"><lem>諸</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>阿羅漢。汝等<note n="0783010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">疾＝速【聖】</note><app n="0783010"><lem>疾</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">速</rdg></app>往大海渚上。取牛頭
<lb n="0783a18"/>栴檀種種香木。即<note n="0783011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">受教&CB00330;＝便受教【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783011" resp="CBETA" type="mod">受教&CB00330;＝便受教【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783011"><lem>受教&CB00330;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">便受教</rdg></app>。如彈指頃。各到
<lb n="0783a19"/>大海。共取香薪。屈伸臂頃。便<app type="＊" source="0782025"><lem>已</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">以</rdg></app>來到。佛與
<lb n="0783a20"/>大眾。共積香薪。舉棺置上。放火焚之。一切
<lb n="0783a21"/>大眾。見火<note n="0783012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盛＝熾【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783012" resp="CBETA" type="mod">盛＝熾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783012"><lem>盛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">熾</rdg></app>然。<note n="0783013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皆＋（同）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">皆＋（同）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783013"><lem>皆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">皆同</rdg></app>向佛前。宛轉自撲。益
<lb n="0783a22"/>更悲哭。有得道者。皆<note n="0783014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">自＝悉【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">自＝悉【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783014"><lem>自</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">悉</rdg></app>慶幸。未獲道者。心
<lb n="0783a23"/><note n="0783015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">戰＝顫【元】【明】</note><app n="0783015"><lem>戰</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">顫</rdg></app>惶怖。衣毛為&CB00594;</p>
<lb n="0783a24"/><p><note n="0783016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">爾時＝於是【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">爾時＝於是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783016"><lem>爾時</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">於是</rdg></app>世尊。告<note n="0783017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">眾會＝大眾【三】【宮】，四眾會【聖】</note><note n="0783017" resp="CBETA" type="mod">眾會＝大眾【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝四眾會【聖】</note><app n="0783017"><lem>眾會</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">大眾</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">四眾會</rdg></app>曰。世皆無常。苦空非身。
<lb n="0783a25"/>無有堅固。如幻如化。如熱時炎。如水中月。
<lb n="0783a26"/>命不久居。汝等諸人。勿見此火。便以為熱。
<lb n="0783a27"/>諸欲之火。極復過此。是故<note n="0783018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">汝等當＝當勤而【三】【宮】</note><note n="0783018" resp="CBETA" type="mod">汝等當＝當勤而【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0783018"><lem>汝等。當</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">當勤而</rdg></app>自勸勉。
<lb n="0783a28"/><note n="0783019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">永離＝求離【聖】</note><app n="0783019"><lem>永離</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">求離</rdg></app>生死。乃得大安。<note n="0783020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時＝是【宮】</note><app n="0783020"><lem>時</lem><rdg wit="【宮】" resp="Taisho">是</rdg></app>火焚燒大王身已。
<lb n="0783a29"/>爾時諸王。各各皆持五百瓶乳。以用滅火。火
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0512.0783b" n="0783b"/>
<lb n="0783b01"/>滅之後。競共收骨。盛置金&CB00630;。即於其上。便
<lb n="0783b02"/>共起塔。懸繒幡蓋及種種鈴供養塔廟。時諸
<lb n="0783b03"/>大眾。同時發聲。俱白佛言。大淨飯王。今已
<lb n="0783b04"/>命終。神生何所。唯願世尊。分別解說。於<note n="0783021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時火焚燒＝焚【宮】</note><note n="0783021" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><todo/>時火焚燒＝焚【宮】</note>時
<lb n="0783b05"/>世尊。告眾會曰。父王淨飯。是清淨人。生淨
<lb n="0783b06"/><note n="0783022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">居天眾會＝居天【宋】【明】【宮】，世界【元】</note><note n="0783022" resp="CBETA" type="mod">居天眾會＝居天【宋】【明】【宮】，＝世界【元】</note><app n="0783022"><lem>居天。<note n="0783023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔眾會〕－【聖】</note><app n="0783023"><lem>眾會</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">居天</rdg><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">世界</rdg></app>聞是語已。便捨愁毒。佛說經
<lb n="0783b07"/>竟。諸天龍神。及四天王。所將眷屬。世間人
<lb n="0783b08"/>民。一切大眾為佛作禮各自<note n="0783024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">還＝而【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0783024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">還＝而【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0783024"><lem>還</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">而</rdg></app>去</p></div1>
